            "body": "That makes sense. I think it would help if the enabler also worked client-wise and not just buffer-wise. Also, the issue title might be a bit misleading, because in terms of functionality, document colors are indeed only enabled for clients that support the requests. This is just done inside the enable() logic. Is it possible to just use `supports_method` here to see which clients have enabled document color?",
