            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "@matystroia the reason why we enable `document_color` in `lsp.lua` without checking for the capabilities is because [this is one of the few features that we currently have dynamic registration for](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/33800). If the server registers the capability after initialization, then we wouldn't enable the feature.",
